*Nedostaje* mi tebe. (I miss you.)
Nešto *nedostaje* u ovoj slikari. (Something is missing in this painting.)
Neophodno *nedostaje* još mnogo rada. (A lot of work is still needed.)
Dobro je što je *nedostajuća* stvar pronađena. (It's good that the missing thing has been found.)
Njegova *nedostajanja* su se osećala. (His absences were felt.)